0.content: See the files /assets/tests/search-data-jekyll-*.json, copied from the files generated from /assets/js/zzzz-search-data.json with different versions of Jekyll. Jekyll-3.8.7 and 4.1.1 produce the expected content with rendered search data. Jekyll-4.2.0 (run locally) produces content with unrendered search data.
